<p id=post_heading>
Linux Kya Hay?
</p>
Linux Ek Operating System hay. Operating System Matlab Jayse ham Windows use karte hay to windows XP ek operating system hay aor windows 7 bhi operating system hay. Operating system computer ki basic needs hay. Operating system ke bina koi user computer start nahi kar sakta. Jayse windows OS(operating system) hay wayse hi Linux bhi OS hay. Jayse windows ke alag alag version hay (windows XP, windows 7, windows 8, windows vista, etc...) vayse hi linux ke bhi alag alga version hay (Ubuntu, Linux Mint, Cent OS, Kubuntu, Trisqule, etc...). Kisi bhi software ko run karne ke liye OS installed hona jaruri hay. Linux os ek fast aor secure OS hay. 
<br><p id=post_heading>
Linux Kyu Use kare?
</p>
Aksar Windows me virus ki problem raheti hay. Jiske liye anti virus lagana padta hay lekin uske bad bhi kuch virus ka khatara to raheta hi hay. Lekin Linux me virus ki koi problem nahi hoti. Linux windows se jyada secure hay. May Last 2 year se linux hi use kar raha hau aor aaj tak usme koi problem nahi hui. windows me kuch time ke bad speed slow hoti jati hay lekin linux me aaysa nahi hota. Linux me kuch problems bhi hay par firbhi linux windows se behtar OS hay. Niche Mayne linux ke Fayede aor nuksan dikhaye hay.
<br>
